Title: Into the Night
Writer: Adam Todd, Reg Watson (creator), Lara Radulovich (creator)
Actors: Danielle Cormack, Nicole da Silva, Kate Atkinson, Celia Ireland
Plot: As Bea and Franky go to war for control of the prison, Bea puts her daring plan in motion. Meanwhile, Fletch is on a downward spiral of self-destructive behaviour as his final day at Wentworth looms.
